    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >26-year-old Henry is at friend's halloween party. At 11pm they sit down at the table and tell each other terrible stories. Henry begins to tell a terrifying story from his life when he was just a little boy...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play the role of little Henry and experience the terror that befell him 20 years earlier on Halloween. The game consists one quick chapter (due to the cancellation of the game development).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are in your childhood home 20 years earlier. Your job is to stay alive and keep the Devil, who wants your soul, away from you. Surviving the day will be a challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be up to the task?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It Depends On You.</p>",
